title: Spotify Mood Explorer
description: Built an interactive web dashboard that clustered 170K+ Spotify tracks into mood-based groups using machine learning (PCA + K-Means) and integrated the Spotify API for real-time song exploration and visualization.

title: Exploring Food Trends
description: Developed an end-to-end ML pipeline on 83K+ recipes and 230K+ reviews to analyze food trends, predict protein content with regression models (RÂ² = 0.84), and evaluate fairness across dietary groups.

title: A/B Testing with SQL & Python
description: Designed and executed an A/B test analysis using SQL and Python to measure conversion rate differences between page versions, applying statistical hypothesis testing and visualization to determine significance.
